## 10. Debug & Troubleshooting

### Quick diagnostics
```bash
curl -sf http://localhost:8000/health
bash scripts/smoke-test.sh
docker compose -f infra/docker-compose.yml logs api --tail 50
```

### Decision tree
```
401 → invalid key / JWT expired / DEV_API_KEY in production
403 → agent-scoped key mismatch on agent= param
400 search/context → OPENAI_API_KEY or Settings → Embeddings
Log works, search empty → events logged before embedding key configured
Baseline insufficient_data / warming_up → add session_id; need session volume
why() 404 → wrong event_id or other tenant
Does not wrap LLM — add db.log() at decision points; parent_id for causality
Not a Pinecone replacement — agent decision history; many teams use both
Other embedding providers → roadmap (today: OpenAI only in code)
```

### Do not claim (product / marketing)
- Real-time alerting everywhere (baseline exists; alerting may be partial/roadmap)
- Replaces full observability stack (complements APM/logs)
- Detects hallucinations (drift is behavioral statistics)
- SOC2 / HIPAA certified unless explicitly launched
- Works offline (needs API reachability, or self-host on localhost)

### Dashboard pipeline test
```bash
curl -X POST http://localhost:8000/v1/auth/dev-token
curl -X POST http://localhost:8000/v1/auth/test-event -H "Authorization: Bearer <jwt>"
```

### Useful curl
```bash
curl -H "Authorization: Bearer $KEY" http://localhost:8000/v1/agents
curl -H "Authorization: Bearer $KEY" "http://localhost:8000/v1/events?agent=my-bot&limit=5"
curl -H "Authorization: Bearer $KEY" "http://localhost:8000/v1/events/$EVENT_ID/why"
```

